span><span class=\"space\"> </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">{</span><span class=\"space\"> </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">ref</span><span class=\"space\"> </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">}</span><span class=\"space\"> </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">=</span><span class=\"space\"> </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">Vue</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#A0ADA0;--shiki-dark:#758575DD\">//</span><span class=\"space\"> </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#A0ADA0;--shiki-dark:#758575DD\">...</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">const</span><span class=\"space\"> </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">num</span><span class=\"space\"> </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">=</span><span class=\"space\"> </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\">ref</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">(</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#2F798A;--shiki-dark:#4C9A91\">0</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">);</span></span></code></pre>\n\n<div class=\"line-numbers\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"counter-reset:line-number 0\"><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div></div></div><p>因为是一个响应式的可变对象，需要改变<code v-pre>num</code>的值的时候通过改变<code v-pre>num.value</code>来改变它。</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>推荐一种写法：只有我们明确知道要转换的对象内部的字段名称我们才使用 <code v-pre>reactive()</code>，否则就一律使用 <code v-pre>ref()</code>，从而降低在语法选择上的心理负担。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"_6-3-torefs-函数\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#_6-3-torefs-函数\"><span>6.3 toRefs() 函数</span></a></h3>\n<p><code v-pre>reactive()</code> 函数处理后的返回对象